[package]
name = "ts-rs"
version = "8.1.0"
authors = [ "Moritz Bischof <moritz.bischof1@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT"
description = "generate typescript bindings from rust types"
homepage = "https://github.com/Aleph-Alpha/ts-rs"
repository = "https://github.com/Aleph-Alpha/ts-rs"
keywords = [ "typescript", "ts", "bindings", "ts-rs", "wasm",]
categories = [ "development-tools::ffi", "development-tools::build-utils", "wasm", "web-programming",]
readme = "../README.md"
rust-version = "1.63.0"

[features]
chrono-impl = [ "chrono",]
bigdecimal-impl = [ "bigdecimal",]
uuid-impl = [ "uuid",]
bson-uuid-impl = [ "bson",]
bytes-impl = [ "bytes",]
url-impl = [ "url",]
serde-compat = [ "ts-rs-macros/serde-compat",]
format = [ "dprint-plugin-typescript",]
default = [ "serde-compat",]
indexmap-impl = [ "indexmap",]
ordered-float-impl = [ "ordered-float",]
heapless-impl = [ "heapless",]
semver-impl = [ "semver",]
serde-json-impl = [ "serde_json",]
no-serde-warnings = [ "ts-rs-macros/no-serde-warnings",]
import-esm = []

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1"

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1"

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dev-dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.heapless]
version = ">= 0.7, < 0.9"
optional = true

[dependencies.ts-rs-macros]
version = "=8.1.0"
path = "../macros"

[dependencies.dprint-plugin-typescript]
version = "0.90"
optional = true

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.bigdecimal]
version = ">= 0.0.13, < 0.5"
features = [ "serde",]
optional = true

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.bson]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.bytes]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.url]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.semver]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.indexmap]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.ordered-float]
version = ">= 3, < 5"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1"
optional = true

[package]
name = "ts-rs-macros"
version = "8.1.0"
authors = [ "Moritz Bischof <moritz.bischof1@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
description = "derive macro for ts-rs"
license = "MIT"
homepage = "https://github.com/Aleph-Alpha/ts-rs"
repository = "https://github.com/Aleph-Alpha/ts-rs"

[features]
serde-compat = [ "termcolor",]
no-serde-warnings = []

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1"
quote = "1"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0.28"
features = [ "full", "extra-traits",]

[dependencies.termcolor]
version = "1"
optional = true
